(20,'native plant cell','A plant cell that is either part of a multicellular whole plant in vivo or a unicellular organism in natura (i.e. part of a natural environment).','microgametophyte vegetative cell','A native plant cell that is the larger cell of a microgametophyte in seed plants. It does not divide further and develops into a pollen tube cell.'),
