(22,'native plant cell','A plant cell that is either part of a multicellular whole plant in vivo or a unicellular organism in natura (i.e. part of a natural environment).','plant gamete','A native plant cell that has half the chromosome complement of the sporophyte and is capable of fertilization to create a plant zygote.'),
